# Machine-local project state (the live autosave slot + any *.local saves). The live
# project is written automatically on every authoritative edit for crash recovery; it is
# runtime state, not source, so it is never committed. Mirrors the repo's *.local.json
# convention. Plain named saves (projects/<name>.json) are intentionally NOT ignored.
projects/*.local.json

# Project backups (#123): local snapshot bundles + the off-site outbox mirror. Runtime state,
# regenerated on every boot/cadence/pre-risk trigger — never committed.
projects/backups/
projects/backups-outbox.jsonl
